# 10. もっともっと届けたい

Ichika: That was great, Minori! I really liked your singing and dancing.
Minori: Th-Thanks! Hehe. I wasn't sure what would happen after I made so many mistakes early on...
Minori: I'm just wondering if I was able to spread any hope to anyone watching...
Nene: Yeah, I'm sure you did...
Kohane: You had this idol aura about you too! I really think you've taken a big step towards catching up with the other girls in your group!
Minori: R-Really?!
Minori: Hehe. I sure hope so...!
Ichika: Good for you, Minori...
Ichika: I'm glad I got to perform here today too. I feel like I was able to show just how appreciative I am...
Nene: Yeah, me too. I doubt I'll ever forget what I experienced today.
Kohane: I think we all feel the same way about today...!
Minori: Yeah...! Thank you so much, everyone!
Toya: Azusawa's performance was really something else.
Akito: Yeah, the others were pretty good too. They all found a way to get this crowd going.
An: Yeah, I should've signed up for this too!
Kohane: Oh, there you all are...!
An: Kohane...! You were off the hook today!
Toya: I agree. Well done, Azusawa.
An: Don't you have anything to say, Akito?
Akito: I mean, she did what she usually does. Just stay focused for the next event, okay?
An: Oh, is that how it's gonna be...? Who was the showering with praise just a second ago?
Akito: You tell me.
Toya: Hehe...
Akito: Quit laughing, Toya!
Kohane: Hehe. Thank you, all of you! I'll promise to do my best during our next event too!
Saki: Ichi, that was awesome! Like, really super awesome!
Ichika: Thanks...! I don't know what to say.
Ichika: I was a little nervous but it ended up being a worthwhile experience.
Nene: S-So... How did I do...?
Emu: Really really really really super wonderhoy! I got goosebumps everywhere!
Tsukasa: She's right! And we should expect no less from our songstress! Everyone was absolutely blown away by your performance!
Nene: Th-Thanks...
Nene: (But I still have a lot left to work on, including some things I discovered today.)
Nene: (Still, I sang up there all by myself, so I feel like I took a big step towards becoming a musical actress...)
Minori: ...
Minori: (My heart won't stop. It almost feels like I'm dreaming too.)
Minori: (I actually did a performance all on my own...)
Airi: Hey, found her! Minori! We've been looking all over for you!
Minori: Oh, hi...! Sorry, my mind's still trying to process what just happened...
Shizuku: We all understand exactly how you feel. After all, this was your very first solo performance.
Minori: Y-You do...?
Haruka: Yes, and you did great...! Like a true idol.
Minori: H-Haruka...!
Airi: But there's still a lot we need to work on. We'll get started on that when we get back!
Minori: Eep...
Shizuku: Hehe. It was still a wonderful performance. Your smile and optimism likely helped inspire hope in everyone that came to watch today.
Airi: Yeah, true. I can't give it a 100, but it warrants at least an 80.
Minori: Really...?!
Minori: I know I'm still nowhere near you guys yet, but I feel like I took a big step forward today...!
Minori: And I hope we can keep moving forward as a group!
Haruka: I'm sure we will. We wouldn't be “MORE MORE JUMP!” without you here, Minori.
Ena: Hey, Airi!
Airi: Oh, Ena, perfect timing! You should meet Minori.
Shizuku: Oh, that's right!
Minori: Wait, huh?
Airi: Everyone, allow me to introduce you all to our star idol, Minori Hanasato!
Minori: H-Hello! My name is Minori Hanasato! It's nice to meet you all!
Ena: Nice to meet you too! I'm Ena Shinonome. Airi's told me all about you.
Mizuki: Oh, me next! I'm Mizuki Akiyama! Nice to meet you, Minori!
Mizuki: We saw your performance too! It was so awesome! You really shined up there! Starting today, I'm officially your fan!
Minori: Th-Thank you so much! W-Wait, my fan...?!
Mizuki: Of course! How can I not become your fan after seeing you sing?!
Mizuki: I'll make sure to check out your old streams too! And when you make it big, I can say that it was all thanks to me!
Ena: Wait, that's your angle...?
Ena: Oh, Minori, I almost forgot. Meet Kanade and Mafuyu. They're also a part of our little music group.
Mafuyu: Nice to meet you. My name is Mafuyu Asahina. Your performance today was incredible, Hanasato. I'll be sure to keep an eye out for your stream from now on.
Kanade: Oh, um... I'm Kanade Yoisaki... I really liked your performance too.
Kanade: It was so... Bright...
Minori: *Gasp* Thank you very much...!
Minori: (My dance didn't go as planned, and I'm still nowhere near everyone else's level yet...)
Minori: (But I performed in front of a lot of people and even got praised for my performance... As an idol...!)
Minori: (I want to keep practicing and keep spreading hope with Haruka and the others to all our fans.)
Minori: Alright! I'm gonna keep trying more and more and more!
